data.description: Welcome Home! 111 Friendship Pointe is a 5 bed/3 bath home just minutes from access to Lake Hartwell and Clemson University, as well as shopping, dining, and interstate access! Located on a private lot that is just under one acre, this spacious home offers the privacy and layout you have been looking for! Inside you will find a sunny open floor plan complete with a two-story foyer, formal living and dining rooms, two story Great Room and roomy kitchen. Extra touches include LVP flooring throughout most of the main floor living space and in the primary bedroom, archways into the formal living, dining and kitchen areas, and a security system with cameras that conveys with the home.  The kitchen features granite countertops, center island, large pantry, and plenty of cabinet space. Transition through the breakfast area to the Great Room that overlooks the private backyard. Off the Great Room is a guest room (or great home office space!) as well as the first of three full baths. Rounding out the main floor is the walk-in laundry area and access to the two car garage. Upstairs is a catwalk overlooking the main floor along with three additional secondary bedrooms that share a well-appointed hall bath. The primary suite is also on the second floor and features a trey ceiling, sitting area, and full bath with granite countertops, dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet. The outside living space offers a tranquil place to birdwatch, spy on deer in the edge of the trees, plant gardens, add a pool…the possibilities are truly endless. The long street ends in a cul de sac so there is limited traffic making it a great place to ride bikes, jog, or walk the dog. Friendship Boat Ramp is less than ten minutes away and features a two-lane launching ramp, restrooms, designated swim beach, picnic area, courtesy dock, and playground! Fall is in the air and that means changing leaves, cooler nights, and football season-and 111 Friendship Pointe is ready and waiting for you!
